column2: SELECT TOP # p.specObjID, zs.nvote, zs.p_el as elliptical, zs.p_cw as spiralclock, zs.p_acw as spiralanticlock, zs.p_edge as edgeon, zs.p_dk as dontknow, zs.p_mg as merger FROM galSpecLine as p JOIN ZooSpec AS zs ON p.specObjID = zs.specobjid JOIN Galaxy as y ON p.specObjID = y.specObjID WHERE zs.nvote > = # and zs.p_acw > #
